AcFun (simplified Chinese: AcFun弹幕视频网; traditional Chinese: AcFun彈幕視頻網; pinyin: AcFun dàn mù shì pín wǎng), known as AC for short, is a Chinese video sharing website. AcFun is an abbreviation of "Anime, Comic and Fun". It is the first video sharing website which comments are overlaid on videos. The website is initially targeted towards an ACGN(Animation, Comic, Game and Novel) audience, and is currently one of the more influential video sharing website for its target audience. AC Musume and TD Musume are the representative icons of AcFun.


